OWAYENGUMENGAMELI wakuleli, uMnuz Jacob Zuma, uthi usekulungele ukuqulwa kwecala lenkohlakalo abhekene nalo nenkampani yaseFrance, iThales, nakuba leli cala liphinde lahlehliswa ngenxa yesicelo ahlongoza ukusifaka enkantolo. Bebephume ngobuningi babo abalandeli bakaZuma ukuzomeseka ngesikhathi evela eNkantolo eNkulu, eMgungundlovu, ngoMsombuluko. Kulokhu bekukhona nobuholi be-ANC eKZN ngempelasonto okuvele izindaba zokuthi bukhethe ukumeseka kuleli cala. Ngesikhathi kulindeleke ukuthi kubonakale ufakazi wokuqala kuleli cala, uNkk Patricia De Lille, uMshushisi, uBilly Downer, uveze ukuthi abameli abasha bakaZuma sebeveze ukuthi bazofaka isicelo sokuthi ahoxe kuleli cala. Izizathu zalokhu azibekwanga enkantolo kodwa uJaji Piet Koen ubavumelile ukuthi bafake isicelo sabo enkantolo ngoLwesithathu kuleli sonto bese umbuso uyaphendula, yena uyobe esememezela isinqumo sakhe kulolu daba ngoMeyi 26. Ekhuluma ngaphandle kwenkantolo kubalandeli bakhe, uMnuz Jacob Zuma ubabongile ngokumeseka, wagqugquzela ubumbano kwi-ANC ekhuza labo abebehhahhameza abaholi be-ANC KwaZulu-Natal, uMnuz Sihle Zikalala, noMnuz Mdumiseni Ntuli. Uthe ngisho naye kunabantu afike aphikisane nabo ngasese kodwa bayakufihla lokho uma sebekhuluma esidlangalaleni ngoba akafuni ukujabulisa izitha. Nakuba icala lihlehlile, uZuma uthe usekulungele ukuthi kuqale ukuqulwa kwalo kodwa ufuna ukuqinisekisa ukuthi liqulwa ngaphansi kwezimo ezihambisana nomthethosisekelo. Thola udaba olugcwele kwiSolezwe ngoLwesibili. 